ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend the course. Very helpful introduction to the material you need to know as a grad student.

The recommendations sections doesn't quite fit for this course given it is mandatory, but if someone could choose to take it I'd definitely recommend it. It was a great survey of thinkers in analytic philosophy and I learned a ton.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Most of the thinkers and all of the books covered I had not studied in much of any depth before the course. I learned an enormous amount that I'm sure will be a good foundation in which to support my studies.
